⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Lysandra
node M1 · M1 · ⟦Lysandra:M1:25469f⟧

WHO   — Lysandra — the courtesan of Rifthold
WHAT  — Celaena's social adversary in The Assassin's Blade — the lovely, spiteful favorite whose claim on Arobynn's attention and on Rifthold's finery makes her the assassin's chosen enemy among the Guild's hangers-on.
WHERE — M1 · Maas  Framework inputs: Throne of Glass — The Assassin's Blade  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because in the salons and silks of Rifthold a girl's worth is measured in beauty, patronage, and favor; because a courtesan climbs by charm and cruelty alike; because nothing wounds a rival like being looked down upon.
HOW   — By her looks and her cultivated grace, by Clarisse's training and Arobynn's indulgence, by sharp little barbs and a talent for making Celaena feel watched, judged, and disdained.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Let the assassin have her blades — I have all of Rifthold looking at me.

